          "content": "★ RECOMMENDED — This is the Slack/Discord pattern refined for Gloam. Quick reactions are the #1 use case for hover actions, and having reply+edit inline eliminates the need for right-click for 90% of interactions.",
          "lineHeight": 1.5,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "500"
        }
      ]
    },
